269
00:29:21,792 --> 00:29:23,672
Nobody owns me!

270
00:29:25,032 --> 00:29:27,192
That's the difference
between me and you.

271
00:29:28,472 --> 00:29:29,752
Lauren!

272
00:29:50,712 --> 00:29:52,512
Take the job, Lauren.

273
00:29:52,912 --> 00:29:55,232
