and for what?

275
00:29:57,072 --> 00:29:59,992
Your story about these women
is just not worth it.

276
00:30:00,832 --> 00:30:02,512
Not worth it?

277
00:30:02,512 --> 00:30:04,472
I forgot. They're just Mexican women
so they're not worth it.

278
00:30:04,472 --> 00:30:06,272
I didn't mean it that way.

279
00:30:07,512 --> 00:30:09,152
Do you see this?

280
00:30:10,232 --> 00:30:11,512
And this?

281
00:30:13,072 --> 00:30:16,912
And this? And this? And this?

282
00:30:18,152 --> 00:30:22,112
All of it is assembled in Juarez
and it's all covered with blood.

283
00:30:22,112 --> 00:30:24,312
Would you calm down?
If you walk out of here today...

284
00:30:24,312 --> 00:30:26,232
